      <title>韩国航空官员警告称，朝鲜垃圾气球将给飞机带来危险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/north-korea-s-trash-balloons-can-endanger-airplanes-aviation-official-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名航空官员警告称，朝鲜的垃圾气球可能对航班构成威胁。前一天，韩国最繁忙的机场因至少一只气球降落在停机坪上而暂停运营。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/north-korea-s-trash-balloons-can-endanger-airplanes-aviation-official-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:08:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒梅尔称法国额外获得 30 亿欧元税收</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/le-maire-says-france-pulled-in-extra-eu3-billion-in-tax-receipts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔表示，税收收入高于预期，增强了法国国库的实力，预计在第一轮立法选举前几天，法国经济形势将更加乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/le-maire-says-france-pulled-in-extra-eu3-billion-in-tax-receipts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 06:24:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 Indeed 招聘信息中提供的薪酬自 1 月份以来上涨最多</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-pay-offered-in-indeed-job-postings-rises-most-since-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国企业在招聘岗位上以自一月份以来最快的速度上调工资，这成为持续通胀压力的一个来源，可能会使降息变得更加复杂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/uk-pay-offered-in-indeed-job-postings-rises-most-since-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国宣布召开重要改革会议，强调党的领导</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-to-hold-delayed-party-meeting-on-reform-from-july-15-to-18</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日召开延期的高层官员会议，预计将就一系列经济和政治问题制定长期政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/china-to-hold-delayed-party-meeting-on-reform-from-july-15-to-18</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:39:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级游说者认为伦敦将在法国和美国大选中占据优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/top-lobbyist-sees-london-gaining-edge-with-france-us-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦一家顶级游说团体的首席执行官表示，由于法国和美国的政治动荡使英国在全球舞台上看起来更具有竞争力，金融巨头们再次寻求在伦敦投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/top-lobbyist-sees-london-gaining-edge-with-france-us-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多数泰国人支持将大麻重新列为麻醉品的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/majority-of-thais-back-plan-to-label-cannabis-as-narcotics-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国政府的一项民意调查显示，绝大多数受访者支持这个东南亚国家将大麻重新归类为麻醉品以禁止其娱乐性使用的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/majority-of-thais-back-plan-to-label-cannabis-as-narcotics-again</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:40:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国参议院选举：退役将军和学者胜出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/former-generals-academics-emerge-winners-in-thai-senate-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国已完成选举新一届参议院（共 200 名议员）的复杂程序，新一届参议院的权力将小于即将离任的上议院，一些前军官、警官和学者将成为获胜者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/former-generals-academics-emerge-winners-in-thai-senate-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理银行借了巨额债务。现在 1600 万泰晤士水务用户正在为此买单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thames-water-users-left-to-pick-up-bill-for-former-owner-macquarie</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这家澳大利亚集团管理的基金在十年内盈利约 16.5 亿英镑。这家负债累累的英国水务公司目前濒临破产——而下一届政府面临着拯救它的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/thames-water-users-left-to-pick-up-bill-for-former-owner-macquarie</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 04:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国左翼势力摇摆不定 奥朗德提议组建联合政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/france-s-hollande-mulls-unity-government-as-his-left-bloc-creaks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国前总统弗朗索瓦·奥朗德表示，如果选举产生悬浮议会，他将准备组建一个新的执政联盟，他加入的左翼阵营是为了掩盖内部分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/france-s-hollande-mulls-unity-government-as-his-left-bloc-creaks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 21:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默否认苏纳克在英国最后辩论中取得明显胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/starmer-vows-to-reset-politics-in-final-debate-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 承诺解决英国停滞的经济和疲软的公共服务问题，而基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 则指责苏纳克“脱离选民”，首相则利用下周大选前的最后一场电视辩论，在税收问题上攻击在民意调查中领先的对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-26/starmer-vows-to-reset-politics-in-final-debate-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:27:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
